<br>
GRAVE<br>
<br>
If the person buried lived a good life, flowers will grow on the grave. If the person was evil, weeds will grow. <br>
<br>
***Well, most of the people I know who have died have grass growing on their graves unless flowers have been brought of planted. I wonder what that means? <br>
